snippet.title: Pokémon GO | Season of Heritage
snippet.description:
In the next Pokémon GO Season, we’ll look to the past for answers that will help guide us into the future of Pokémon GO! 

Join us as we take our Pokémon GO adventure into the Season of Heritage! 
Discover more by visiting the Season of Heritage web page: https://pokemongolive.com/seasons/heritage
